name: Harley Quinn
story: Harley Quinn is making a name for herself in the villian community after leaving the Joker.

name: Thanos
story: Thanos is back after being defeated by the Avengers to set balance to the Earth.

name: Joker
story: The Joker's origin is somewhat of a mystery, although it's known that he fell into a vat of chemicals. He's been after Batman ever since.

name: Agatha Harkness
story: Agatha Harkness was accused of practicing dark magic by her coven hundreds of years ago in Salem, sensing the Scarlett Witch's magic she had to come.

name: Poison Ivy
story: Poison Ivy, also know as Pamela Isley, is plant enthusiast turned super villian who got her plant powers from some experiments.

name: Venom
story: Venom is a symbiote from planet Klyntar who merged with Eddie Brock after coming to Earth.
